sections.History:
===[[Season 1]]===
[[Viserys Targaryen]] tells [[Doreah]] about how the [[House Targaryen|Targaryens]] flew from Valyria to conquer Westeros. He describes Valyria as the greatest civilization in the history of the world.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Cripples, Bastards and Broken Things]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt; At Khal [[Drogo]]'s funeral pyre, as [[Daenerys Targaryen]] prepares to walk into the fires to attempt to hatch her [[dragon]] eggs, she proclaims to her followers that, &quot;I am Daenerys Stormborn, of the House Targaryen, of the blood of Old Valyria. I ''am'' the dragon's daughter.&quot;&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Fire and Blood]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 2]]===
[[File:Quaithe painting.jpg|thumb|Quaithe paints designs of protection on a sailor in &quot;[[A Man Without Honor]]&quot;.]]
When Ser [[Jorah Mormont]] visits [[Quaithe]] in [[Qarth]], she is inking tattoos onto a sailor's back. She says they will protect him as his ship must sail close to the Valyrian coastline, where the Doom still holds sway.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[A Man Without Honor]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
